reviewText:
As usual good production value no skips or jumps and the audio is consistent.

This offering brings us two episodes and a wealth of Special Features

Special Features:
~The Making of The Ultimate Foe
~Deleted and Extended Scenes
~Trails and Continuity
~Trials and Tribulations
~1985 Hiatus
~Doctor in Distress
~Open Air
~Audio Options (Meaning Commentary 1 and Commentary 2 [Episode 13 only])
~Info Text
~Saturday Superstore
~Photo Gallery
~PDF Materials
this was a gift for my sister who loves all things Dr. Who and actually didn't have this one.  She is thrilled
